Telecom New Zealand Says Some Network Sites Badly Damaged by Earthquake

-- B y   T i m   S m i t h
-- 
2011-02-22T01:19:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-22/telecom-new-zealand-says-some-network-sites-badly-damaged-by-earthquake.html
Telecom Corp. of  New Zealand  said
some of its network sites were badly damaged by the Christchurch
earthquake and is asking people to only use phones for
emergencies, according to an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
